<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id" class="antialiased">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"/>
  <title><%= config.name %> — Support</title>

  <!-- Tailwind (class-based dark mode) -->
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>tailwind.config = { darkMode: 'class' };</script>

  <!-- Fonts & Icons -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/favicon.png" />
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/img/favicon.png" />
  <style>
    /* --- CSS Variables --- */
    :root { 
      --card-bg: #ffffff; 
      --card-shadow: rgba(2,6,23,0.06); 
      --accent: #6366f1; 
      --accent-2: #4f46e5; 
      --surface: #f8fafc;
      --text-primary: #0f172a;
    }
    
    html,body { 
      font-family:"Montserrat",system-ui,-apple-system,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Arial; 
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    
    body { 
      background: var(--surface); 
      -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; 
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .dark body { 
      background: #071127; 
      --surface: #071127;
      --text-primary: #f1f5f9;
    }

    /* Modern Card Design */
    .card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px var(--card-shadow);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.03);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(2,6,23,0.1);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    
    .dark .card { 
      background: #0b1a3a; 
      --card-shadow: rgba(2,6,23,0.25); 
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); 
    }

    /* Typography Improvements */
    h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    
    .dark h1, .dark h2, .dark h3, .dark h4, .dark h5, .dark h6 {
      color: #f1f5f9;
    }

    /* Utility Classes */
    .mono-box {
      font-family: ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Monaco,"Roboto Mono",monospace;
      background: #f3f4f6;
      padding: .35rem .6rem;
      border-radius: .5rem;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    .dark .mono-box { 
      background: #041127; 
    }

    .status-pill {
      padding: .35rem .6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: inline-flex;
      gap: .5rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      color: white;
      padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      min-width: 140px;
    }
    
    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn-primary[disabled] {
      opacity: .6;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }
    
    .btn-ghost {
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.08);
      padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
      border-radius: 0.875rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      min-width: 120px;
    }
    
    .btn-ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.03);
      border-color: rgba(15,23,42,0.1);
    }
    
    .dark .btn-ghost {
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    
    .dark .btn-ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }

    /* Result Area */
    .result-area {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: .75rem;
      background: #f9fafb;
      transition: all .22s ease; 
      border: 1px solid rgba(2,6,23,0.03);
    }
    
    .dark .result-area { 
      background: #041225; 
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); 
    }

    /* Layout Helpers */
    .page-container { 
      max-width: 1200px; 
      margin-left: auto; 
      margin-right: auto; 
      padding-left: 1.5rem; 
      padding-right: 1.5rem; 
    }
    
    @media (min-width: 1024px) { 
      .page-container { 
        max-width: 1280px; 
      } 
    }
    
    .sticky-sidebar { 
      position: sticky; 
      top: 96px; 
    }

    /* Responsive Tweaks */
    @media (max-width: 768px) { 
      .desktop-only { display: none; } 
    }
    
    @media (min-width: 769px) { 
      .mobile-only { display: none; } 
    }

    /* Form Labels */
    label.form-label { 
      display: block; 
      font-weight: 600; 
      margin-bottom: .5rem; 
      color: var(--text-primary); 
    }
    
    .dark label.form-label { 
      color: #e6eefb; 
    }

    /* Icon Badge */
    .icon-badge { 
      display: inline-flex; 
      align-items: center; 
      justify-content: center; 
      width: 48px; 
      height: 48px; 
      border-radius: .6rem; 
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(99,102,241,0.12), rgba(99,102,241,0.06)); 
      color: var(--accent); 
      font-weight: 700; 
    }

    /* Contact Card */
    .contact-card { 
      border-radius: 1rem; 
      padding: 1.5rem; 
      display: flex; 
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem; 
      border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.04); 
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.7), rgba(255,255,255,0.85)); 
      height: 100%;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .contact-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(2,6,23,0.1);
    }
    
    .dark .contact-card { 
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0b1a3a, #071225); 
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); 
    }

    .contact-actions { 
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    /* Accordion */
    .accordion-item + .accordion-item { 
      margin-top: .5rem; 
    }
    
    .acc-header { 
      cursor: pointer; 
      display: flex; 
      align-items: center; 
      justify-content: space-between; 
      padding: 1rem 1rem; 
      border-radius: .75rem; 
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .acc-header:hover {
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.03);
    }
    
    .dark .acc-header:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }
    
    .acc-body { 
      padding: 0 1rem 1rem; 
    }

    /* Text Styles */
    .small-muted { 
      font-size: .85rem; 
      color: #6b7280; 
    }
    
    .dark .small-muted { 
      color: #9fb0d6; 
    }
    
    /* Improved Header */
    .nav-link {
      position: relative;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .nav-link::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      bottom: -5px;
      left: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      transition: width 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .nav-link:hover::after,
    .nav-link.active::after {
      width: 100%;
    }
    
    /* Mobile Menu Animation */
    #mobile-menu {
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    #mobile-menu.open {
      max-height: 300px;
    }
    
    /* Toast Notification */
    .toast {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 2rem;
      right: 2rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      z-index: 100;
      transform: translateY(100px);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .toast.show {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
    
    .dark .toast {
      background: #1e293b;
    }

    /* Contact Grid Fixes */
    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      .contact-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }
    }

    /* Button Group Fixes */
    .btn-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn-group .btn-primary,
    .btn-group .btn-ghost {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 120px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-900 text-gray-800 dark:text-slate-100">

  <!-- ========== HEADER ========== -->
  <header class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 sticky top-0 z-40 shadow-sm transition-colors duration-300">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-pink-500 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
    <img src="/img/favlogo.jpg" alt="Logo" class="rounded-lg w-full h-full object-contain" />
  </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-100"><%= config.name %> <span class="hidden text-blue-600 font-semibold">.</span></div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-300 -mt-1">Top Up — Cepat & Aman</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <button id="mobile-theme-toggle" class="md:hidden p-2 rounded-full focus:outline-none hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-700" aria-label="Ubah tema" data-mobile-theme-toggle>
          <i id="mobile-theme-icon" class="fa-solid fa-moon text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-200"></i>
        </button>

        <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 nav-link focus-outline">Beranda</a>
          <a href="/status" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 nav-link focus-outline">Status Pesanan</a>
          <a href="/faq" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 nav-link focus-outline">Faq</a>
          <a href="/panduan" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 nav-link focus-outline">Panduan</a>
          <a href="/syarat-dan-ketentuan" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 nav-link focus-outline">Syarat & Ketentuan</a>
        </nav>

        <button id="theme-toggle" aria-label="Ubah mode: gelap / terang" role="switch" aria-checked="false"
          class="hidden md:inline-flex ml-1 p-1 rounded-full focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-blue-300 bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-600 shadow-sm items-center gap-2">
          <span class="sr-only">Toggle theme</span>
          <span id="theme-icon" class="flex items-center justify-center w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-yellow-400 to-orange-400 text-white shadow icon-rotate">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-sun"></i>
          </span>
        </button>

        <button id="menu-toggle" class="p-2 rounded-md md:hidden focus:outline-none" aria-label="Buka menu">
          <i class="fas fa-bars text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-200"></i>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="mobile-menu" class="md:hidden hidden border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800">
      <div class="px-4 py-4 space-y-2">
        <a href="/" class="block py-2 px-2 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700">Beranda</a>
        <a href="/status" class="block py-2 px-2 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700">Status Pesanan</a>
        <a href="/faq" class="block py-2 px-2 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700">Faq</a>
        <a href="/panduan" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 nav-link focus-outline">Panduan</a>
        <a href="/syarat-dan-ketentuan" class="block py-2 px-2 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700">Syarat & Ketentuan</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>
  <!-- ========== /HEADER ========== -->

  <!-- ========== MAIN: Support page - FIXED LAYOUT ========== -->
  <main class="page-container py-8 md:py-12">
    <!-- Hero Section - Fixed -->
    <div class="mb-8 md:mb-12 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 items-start">
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Butuh Bantuan? <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-pink-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Kami Siap Membantu</span></h1>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">Tim support kami tersedia 24/7 untuk membantu masalah deposit, transaksi, dan layanan lainnya. Pilih kanal komunikasi yang paling nyaman untuk Anda.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4 items-center justify-start lg:justify-end">
        <div class="text-center md:text-right">
          <div class="text-sm small-muted">Waktu Respons</div>
          <div class="font-bold text-lg md:text-xl text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">≤ 2 Jam</div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-100 to-pink-100 dark:from-indigo-900 dark:to-pink-900 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-headset text-lg md:text-xl"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8">
      <!-- Left: contact channels + FAQ -->
      <div class="xl:col-span-3 space-y-6 md:space-y-8">
        <!-- Contact channels - FIXED GRID -->
        <section class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0 md:mr-4">
              <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Hubungi Tim Support</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">Pilih salah satu kanal di bawah untuk menghubungi tim support kami secara langsung.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm small-muted bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-900/20 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300 py-1 px-3 rounded-full self-start">Respons Cepat 24/7</div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-grid mt-6">
            <!-- Email Card -->
            <div class="contact-card">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-14 md:h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-100 to-indigo-200 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 shadow-sm flex-shrink-0">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope text-xl md:text-2xl"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                  <div class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Email</div>
                  <div class="text-sm small-muted mb-2">Untuk laporan & dokumentasi resmi</div>
                  <div class="text-base font-medium truncate"><a id="support-email" href="mailto:<%= config.contact.email %>" class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:underline"><%= config.contact.email %></a></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-auto btn-group">
                <a href="mailto:<%= config.contact.email %>?subject=Support%20Request" class="btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-1">
                  <i class="fa-regular fa-paper-plane mr-2"></i>Kirim Email
                </a>
                <button id="copy-email" class="btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-1">
                  <i class="fa-regular fa-copy mr-2"></i>Salin
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- WhatsApp Card -->
            <div class="contact-card">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-14 md:h-14 rounded-xl bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 shadow-sm flex-shrink-0">
                  <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-xl md:text-2xl"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                  <div class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">WhatsApp</div>
                  <div class="text-sm small-muted mb-2">Obrolan cepat (chat langsung)</div>
                  <div class="text-base font-medium truncate"><a id="support-wa" href="https://wa.me/<%= config.contact.whatsapp %>?text=Hai%20Support%20<%= config.name %>%2C%20saya%20butuh%20bantuan..." target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 hover:underline"><%= config.contact.whatsapp %></a></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-auto btn-group">
                <a id="btn-wa-start" href="https://wa.me/<%= config.contact.whatsapp %>?text=Hai%20Support%20<%= config.name %>%2C%20saya%20butuh%20bantuan..." target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-1">
                  <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp mr-2"></i>Chat via WA
                </a>
                <button id="copy-wa" class="btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-1">
                  <i class="fa-regular fa-copy mr-2"></i>Salin
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Telegram Card -->
            <div class="contact-card">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-14 md:h-14 rounded-xl bg-sky-100 flex items-center justify-center text-sky-600 shadow-sm flex-shrink-0">
                  <i class="fa-brands fa-telegram text-xl md:text-2xl"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                  <div class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Telegram</div>
                  <div class="text-sm small-muted mb-2">Support & notifikasi</div>
                  <div class="text-base font-medium truncate"><a id="support-tg" href="https://t.me/<%= config.contact.telegram %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-400 hover:underline">@<%= config.contact.telegram %></a></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-auto btn-group">
                <a id="btn-tg" href="https://t.me/<%= config.contact.telegram %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-1">
                  <i class="fa-brands fa-telegram mr-2"></i>Buka Telegram
                </a>
                <button id="copy-tg" class="btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-1">
                  <i class="fa-regular fa-copy mr-2"></i>Salin
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- quick note -->
          <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5"><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i></div>
              <div class="text-sm text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">
                <span class="font-semibold">Tips:</span> Untuk respons tercepat, sertakan <strong>ID transaksi / deposit</strong> dan screenshot bila diperlukan.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FAQ accordion -->
        <section class="card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6">Pertanyaan Umum (FAQ)</h3>
          <div class="accordion space-y-4">

            <div class="accordion-item border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <div class="acc-header bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800" data-acc>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">Bagaimana bila deposit belum masuk?</div>
                  <div class="small-muted mt-1">Langkah cepat yang bisa dilakukan</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm small-muted acc-toggle"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down transition-transform"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="acc-body text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300 hidden">
                <p class="mb-3">Periksa ID deposit dan status melalui halaman ini. Jika masih pending lebih dari 30 menit, hubungi support dengan menyertakan:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                  <li>ID deposit</li>
                  <li>Metode pembayaran</li>
                  <li>Waktu transaksi</li>
                  <li>Screenshot bukti pembayaran</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <div class="acc-header bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800" data-acc>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">Apa yang harus disertakan saat menghubungi support?</div>
                  <div class="small-muted mt-1">Mempercepat proses verifikasi</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm small-muted acc-toggle"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down transition-transform"></i></div>
              </div>
              <div class="acc-body text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300 hidden">
                <p class="mb-3">Pastikan untuk mencantumkan informasi berikut:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                  <li>ID transaksi/deposit</li>
                  <li>Metode pembayaran</li>
                  <li>Jumlah transaksi</li>
                  <li>Waktu transaksi</li>
                  <li>Screenshot jika ada</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-3">Semakin lengkap informasi yang diberikan, semakin cepat tim kami dapat merespons.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item border border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <div class="acc-header bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800" data-acc>
